def spacy_ner(x):
  doc = nlp(x)
  entities = []
  labels = []
  for ent in doc.ents:
    entities.append(ent.text)
    labels.append(ent.label_)
  entities_labels = list(zip(entities, labels)) #we do not want unique entities
  return entities_labels

import ast
def get_top_ents(df):

    org_list = list(chain.from_iterable(df['ENT_ORG']))
    counter_org = Counter(org_list)
    top_20_org = counter_org.most_common(20)
    
    prod_list = list(chain.from_iterable(df['ENT_PROD']))
    counter_prod = Counter(prod_list)
    top_20_prod = counter_prod.most_common(20)
    
    per_list = list(chain.from_iterable(df['ENT_PER']))
    counter_per = Counter(per_list)
    top_20_per = counter_per.most_common(20)
    
    norp_list = list(chain.from_iterable(df['ENT_NORP']))
    counter_norp = Counter(norp_list)
    top_20_norp = counter_norp.most_common(20)
    
    loc_list = list(chain.from_iterable(df['ENT_LOC']))
    counter_loc = Counter(loc_list)
    top_20_loc = counter_loc.most_common(20)
    
    return top_20_org, top_20_prod, top_20_per, top_20_norp, top_20_loc

# Combine the occurrences of "Google" and "Googles"
for year in ORG_trend:
    combined_list = []
    for org, count in ORG_trend[year]:
        if org.lower() == "googles":
            combined_list.append(("Google", count))
        elif org.lower() == "nvidia":
            combined_list.append(("NVIDIA", count))
        elif org.lower() in ["chatgpt", 'gpt']:
            combined_list.append(("OpenAI", count))
        elif org.lower() in ['facebook']:
            combined_list.append(("Meta", count))
        else:
            combined_list.append((org, count))
    ORG_trend[year] = combined_list

for year in PER_trend:
    combined_list = []
    for per, count in PER_trend[year]:
        if per.lower() in ["trump", "trumps"]:
            combined_list.append(("Donald Trump", count))
        elif per.lower() == "musk":
            combined_list.append(("Elon Musk", count))
        elif per.lower() == "pichai":
            combined_list.append(("Sundar Pichai", count))
        elif per.lower() in ["biden", "bidens"]:
            combined_list.append(("Joe Biden", count))
        elif per.lower() == "jones":
            combined_list.append(("Rebekah Jones", count))
        elif per.lower() == "gebru":
            combined_list.append(("Timnit Gebru", count))
        elif per.lower() == "altman":
            combined_list.append(("Sam Altman", count))
        else:
            combined_list.append((per, count))
    PER_trend[year] = combined_list
